024/07/shannen-doherty@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shannen-doherty@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shannen-doherty@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露，莎南·多尔蒂在去世前拍摄了五集《<em>魅力》</em>重播播客《<em>哈利韦尔之家》</em> 。</p><p>昨天， <em>House Of Halliwell</em>播客的演员们在社交媒体上宣布了这一消息，确认将发布录制的五集——在这五集期间， <em>《魅力》</em>的演员们会重新观看并讨论该剧。</p><p>此前<i>，</i> 《90210》明星多尔蒂在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/charmed-actress-shannen-doherty-has-reportedly-died-aged-53-3774781"><i>与</i></a>乳腺癌抗争九年后于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/charmed-actress-shannen-doherty-has-reportedly-died-aged-53-3774781"><i>周六</i>（7 月 13 日）去世，享年 53 岁</a>。</p><p> “这个节目、这个角色、这个播客对 Shannen 来说意义重大，她迫不及待地想与世界各地的<em>《Charmed》</em>粉丝分享。我们希望通过播放她去世前录制的前五集来纪念她，并实现莎南的愿望，”该播客在社交媒体上写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9cjzJ2pgLd/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="http